/*  Function      :  Check positive integer                          */
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/*  Parameters    :                                                  */
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/*  Return value  :  Bool                                            */
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/*  Warning       :                                                  */
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/*  Copyright     :                                                  */
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------*/
